  <body dur="03:23.330">
    <div begin="00:01.060" end="03:23.330">
      <p begin="00:01.060" end="00:06.300" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:01.060" end="00:01.420">夜</span><span begin="00:01.420" end="00:02.380">明</span><span begin="00:02.450" end="00:02.620">け</span><span begin="00:02.680" end="00:03.670">を</span><span begin="00:03.820" end="00:03.920">待</span><span begin="00:04.080" end="00:04.830">つ</span><span begin="00:05.180" end="00:05.350">ひ</span><span begin="00:05.520" end="00:06.040">と</span><span begin="00:06.040" end="00:06.300">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">独自等待黎明的人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">獨自等待黎明的人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Alone I wait for dawn</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">새벽을 기다리는 홀로 선 나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Seule à attendre l'aube</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sola esperando el amanecer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Allein warte ich auf die Morgendämmerung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sozinha espero a aurora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Одна я жду рассвета</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Aspetto da sola il sorgere del giorno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yoake o matsu hitori</span></p>
      <p begin="00:06.540" end="00:11.990" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:06.540" end="00:07.800">最</span><span begin="00:07.920" end="00:08.080">後</span><span begin="00:08.190" end="00:08.680">の</span><span begin="00:08.950" end="00:09.270">詩</span><span begin="00:09.300" end="00:09.400">が</span><span begin="00:09.460" end="00:09.670">消</span><span begin="00:09.670" end="00:09.900">え</span><span begin="00:09.990" end="00:10.120">て</span><span begin="00:10.200" end="00:11.990">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">即使最后的诗也消失</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">即使最後的詩也消失</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if the final poem fades away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">마지막 시가 사라져도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si le dernier poème s'efface</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque desaparezca el último poema</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch wenn das letzte Gedicht vergeht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo que o último poema se apague</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже если последняя песнь исчезнет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se la poesia finale svanisce</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Saigo no uta ga kiete mo</span></p>
      <p begin="00:24.670" end="00:34.670" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:24.670" end="00:24.990">世</span><span begin="00:25.070" end="00:25.720">界</span><span begin="00:25.770" end="00:26.340">を</span><span begin="00:26.470" end="00:27.120">眺</span><span begin="00:27.170" end="00:27.260">め</span><span begin="00:27.340" end="00:27.570">て</span><span begin="00:27.670" end="00:28.020">い</span><span begin="00:28.020" end="00:28.440">る</span><span begin="00:28.790" end="00:31.600">今</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">此刻正眺望着世界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">此刻正眺望著世界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Now I am gazing at the world</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">지금 세상을 바라보고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">À cet instant je contemple le monde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ahora contemplo el mundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jetzt blicke ich auf die Welt hinaus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Agora contemplo o mundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сейчас я смотрю на мир</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ora contemplo il mondo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sekai o nagamete iru ima</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:30.210" end="00:34.670"><span begin="00:30.210" end="00:31.480">(窓</span><span begin="00:31.600" end="00:31.850">辺</span><span begin="00:31.960" end="00:32.800">に</span><span begin="00:32.930" end="00:33.180">立</span><span begin="00:33.280" end="00:34.670">ち)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">站在窗边</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">站在窗邊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Standing by the window</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">창가에 서서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Debout près de la fenêtre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">De pie junto a la ventana</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Am Fenster stehend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">De pé junto à janela</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Стоя у окна</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In piedi accanto alla finestra</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Madobe ni tachi</span></span></p>
      <p begin="00:35.650" end="00:44.960" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:35.650" end="00:36.120">始</span><span begin="00:36.240" end="00:36.690">ま</span><span begin="00:36.740" end="00:37.170">る</span><span begin="00:37.410" end="00:37.610">鼓</span><span begin="00:37.770" end="00:38.260">動</span><span begin="00:38.300" end="00:38.500">が</span><span begin="00:38.630" end="00:39.440">鐘</span><span begin="00:39.800" end="00:40.010">の</span><span begin="00:40.140" end="00:40.730">よう</span><span begin="00:40.860" end="00:43.090">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">初生的心跳如钟声一般</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">初生的心跳如鐘聲一般</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The heartbeat beginning like a bell</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">시작되는 고동이 종소리처럼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le battement qui commence comme une cloche</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El latido que comienza como una campana</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der beginnende Herzschlag wie eine Glocke</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O pulsar que começa como um sino</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пробуждающийся пульс словно колокол</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il battito che nasce come una campana</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hajimaru kodou ga kane no you ni</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:41.160" end="00:44.960"><span begin="00:41.160" end="00:42.050">(胸</span><span begin="00:42.220" end="00:42.790">を</span><span begin="00:42.860" end="00:43.130">打</span><span begin="00:43.250" end="00:44.540">つ</span><span begin="00:44.630" end="00:44.960">の)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">敲击着我的胸口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">敲擊著我的胸口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Strikes against my chest</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">가슴을 울려</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Frappe ma poitrine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Golpea mi pecho</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schlägt tief in meiner Brust</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Bate contra o meu peito</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Бьёт мне в грудь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi colpisce il petto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mune o utsu no</span></span></p>
      <p begin="00:45.270" end="00:50.430" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:45.270" end="00:45.780">光</span><span begin="00:45.780" end="00:45.870">を</span><span begin="00:45.970" end="00:46.710">探</span><span begin="00:46.800" end="00:46.930">し</span><span begin="00:47.030" end="00:47.430">て</span><span begin="00:47.700" end="00:48.020">手</span><span begin="00:48.080" end="00:48.380">の</span><span begin="00:48.380" end="00:49.160">赴</span><span begin="00:49.240" end="00:49.600">く</span><span begin="00:49.600" end="00:49.670">ま</span><span begin="00:49.790" end="00:50.430">ま</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">寻找光芒 随手所向</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">尋找光芒 隨手所向</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Searching for light as my hand is led onward</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">빛을 찾아 손이 이끄는 대로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cherchant la lumière au gré de ma main</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Buscando la luz dejo que mi mano avance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auf der Suche nach Licht folge ich meiner Hand</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Buscando a luz deixo a mão seguir seu rumo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В поисках света куда ведёт рука</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Cercando la luce seguo la mano dove vuole andare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hikari o sagashite te no omomuku mama</span></p>
      <p begin="00:51.090" end="00:53.820" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:51.090" end="00:51.480">描</span><span begin="00:51.480" end="00:51.870">い</span><span begin="00:51.970" end="00:52.400">て</span><span begin="00:52.670" end="00:53.180">届</span><span begin="00:53.180" end="00:53.290">い</span><span begin="00:53.360" end="00:53.820">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">描绘吧 抵达吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">描繪吧 抵達吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I draw it may it reach you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그려서 닿아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je dessine pour que cela t'atteigne</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dibuja alcanza</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich zeichne und möge es dich erreichen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Desenho que te alcance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я рисую и дотягиваюсь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Disegna e raggiungi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Egaite todoite</span></p>
      <p begin="00:54.050" end="00:57.020" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:54.050" end="00:54.140">ま</span><span begin="00:54.230" end="00:54.440">だ</span><span begin="00:54.510" end="00:54.670">見</span><span begin="00:54.700" end="00:54.860">ぬ</span><span begin="00:54.860" end="00:55.550">明日</span><span begin="00:55.600" end="00:57.020">へ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">向着仍未见过的明天</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">向著仍未見過的明天</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Toward a tomorrow still unseen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아직 보지 못한 내일로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Vers un demain encore inconnu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hacia un mañana aún no visto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hin zu einem Morgen den ich noch nie gesehen habe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Rumo ao amanhã ainda desconhecido</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">К завтрашнему дню которого ещё не видела</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Un domani ancora mai visto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mada minu ashita e</span></p>
      <p begin="00:57.920" end="01:03.220" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:57.920" end="00:58.280">す</span><span begin="00:58.320" end="00:59.290">ぐ</span><span begin="00:59.330" end="00:59.480">そ</span><span begin="00:59.550" end="01:00.710">ば</span><span begin="01:00.760" end="01:00.960">に</span><span begin="01:00.960" end="01:01.790">あ</span><span begin="01:01.790" end="01:01.860">る</span><span begin="01:02.100" end="01:02.260">も</span><span begin="01:02.290" end="01:02.930">の</span><span begin="01:02.960" end="01:03.220">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">近在身边之物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">近在身邊之物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The things that are right beside me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">바로 곁에 있는 것을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce qui se trouve tout près de moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero saber cómo abrazar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Was doch so nahe bei mir ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero saber como abraçar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">То что совсем рядом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Di ciò che è proprio accanto a me</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sugu soba ni aru mono no</span></p>
      <p begin="01:03.480" end="01:08.700" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="01:03.480" end="01:03.710">抱</span><span begin="01:03.810" end="01:04.760">き</span><span begin="01:04.790" end="01:04.940">し</span><span begin="01:05.040" end="01:06.140">め</span><span begin="01:06.180" end="01:07.470">方</span><span begin="01:07.730" end="01:07.930">知</span><span begin="01:07.930" end="01:08.030">り</span><span begin="01:08.100" end="01:08.210">た</span><span begin="01:08.280" end="01:08.380">く</span><span begin="01:08.460" end="01:08.700">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我想知道该如何拥抱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我想知道該如何擁抱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to learn how to hold them close</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어떻게 끌어안는지 알고 싶어서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je voulais savoir comment l'étreindre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aquello que está tan cerca</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich will wissen wie man es umarmt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Aquilo que está bem ao meu lado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я хочу узнать как обнять</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Vorrei sapere come stringerlo tra le braccia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dakishimekata shiritakute</span></p>
      <p begin="01:08.980" end="01:14.470" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:08.980" end="01:10.360">溢</span><span begin="01:10.360" end="01:10.440">れ</span><span begin="01:10.520" end="01:11.510">出</span><span begin="01:11.510" end="01:11.590">す</span><span begin="01:11.660" end="01:11.820">こ</span><span begin="01:11.870" end="01:12.740">の</span><span begin="01:13.100" end="01:13.890">感</span><span begin="01:13.940" end="01:14.470">情</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这份满溢而出的感情</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這份滿溢而出的感情</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">This feeling overflowing from within</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">흘러넘치는 이 감정</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce sentiment qui déborde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esta emoción que se desborda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dieses Gefühl das aus mir überquillt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esta emoção transbordante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Это чувство что переполняет меня</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Questa emozione che trabocca</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Afuredasu kono kanjou</span></p>
      <p begin="01:14.790" end="01:22.830" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:14.790" end="01:15.110">た</span><span begin="01:15.150" end="01:15.260">だ</span><span begin="01:15.320" end="01:16.110">心</span><span begin="01:16.200" end="01:16.580">に</span><span begin="01:16.830" end="01:17.090">ふ</span><span begin="01:17.090" end="01:17.250">れ</span><span begin="01:17.350" end="01:17.540">た</span><span begin="01:17.580" end="01:18.610">い</span><span begin="01:19.610" end="01:20.510">誰</span><span begin="01:20.600" end="01:22.830">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只想触碰谁的心</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只想觸碰誰的心</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Someone I only wish to touch with my heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그저 마음에 닿고 싶은 누군가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quelqu'un dont je veux seulement toucher le cœur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Alguien que solo quiere tocar un corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eine die nur mein Herz berühren will</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Alguém que eu apenas quero tocar no coração</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Кто то чьего сердца я просто хочу коснуться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Qualcuno che voglia solo toccare il cuore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tada kokoro ni furetai dareka</span></p>
      <p begin="01:32.550" end="01:42.370" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:32.550" end="01:33.020">静</span><span begin="01:33.130" end="01:33.600">か</span><span begin="01:33.670" end="01:34.080">に</span><span begin="01:34.320" end="01:35.010">沈</span><span begin="01:35.010" end="01:35.210">ん</span><span begin="01:35.210" end="01:35.470">で</span><span begin="01:35.540" end="01:35.690">ゆ</span><span begin="01:35.880" end="01:36.370">く</span><span begin="01:36.730" end="01:38.400">夢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">静静沉入深处的梦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">靜靜沉入深處的夢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A dream sinking quietly down</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">조용히 가라앉아 가는 꿈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un rêve qui sombre en silence</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un sueño que se hunde en silencio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Traum sinkt still hinab</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Um sonho afundando em silêncio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сон тихо погружается в глубину</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Un sogno che sprofonda piano</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shizuka ni shizunde yuku yume</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:38.100" end="01:42.370"><span begin="01:38.100" end="01:39.340">(眠</span><span begin="01:39.450" end="01:39.690">り</span><span begin="01:39.830" end="01:40.700">の</span><span begin="01:40.830" end="01:41.010">な</span><span begin="01:41.180" end="01:42.370">か)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在沉眠之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在沉眠之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Within my sleep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">잠 속에서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Au fond du sommeil</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dentro del sueño</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mitten im Schlaf</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Dentro do sono</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Внутри сна</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dentro il sonno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nemuri no naka</span></span></p>
      <p begin="01:43.590" end="01:53.330" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:43.590" end="01:44.020">遠</span><span begin="01:44.130" end="01:44.610">く</span><span begin="01:44.610" end="01:44.960">へ</span><span begin="01:45.310" end="01:45.960">離</span><span begin="01:46.010" end="01:46.090">れ</span><span begin="01:46.170" end="01:46.450">て</span><span begin="01:46.550" end="01:46.710">ゆ</span><span begin="01:46.860" end="01:47.330">く</span><span begin="01:47.690" end="01:48.660">声</span><span begin="01:48.730" end="01:50.780">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">渐渐远去的声音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">漸漸遠去的聲音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A voice drifting far away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">먼 곳으로 멀어져 가는 목소리를</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Une voix qui s'éloigne au loin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La voz que se alejaba hacia lo lejos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eine Stimme die sich in die Ferne verlor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A voz que se afastava para longe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Голос что удалялся вдаль</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La voce che si allontana verso luoghi remoti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tooku e hanarete yuku koe o</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:49.080" end="01:53.330"><span begin="01:49.080" end="01:49.390">(つ</span><span begin="01:49.520" end="01:49.830">な</span><span begin="01:50.100" end="01:50.800">ぎ</span><span begin="01:50.800" end="01:51.080">と</span><span begin="01:51.170" end="01:52.350">め</span><span begin="01:52.470" end="01:53.330">た)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我曾将它系留</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我曾將它繫留</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I held it fast</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">붙잡아 두었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je l'ai retenue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La mantuve unida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hielt ich fest damit sie nicht zerreißt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu prendi para que não se fosse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я удержала чтобы он не оборвался</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Io l ho trattenuta</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsunagitometa</span></span></p>
      <p begin="01:53.180" end="01:58.200" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:53.180" end="01:53.480">何</span><span begin="01:53.540" end="01:53.720">も</span><span begin="01:53.720" end="01:53.840">埋</span><span begin="01:53.910" end="01:54.360">め</span><span begin="01:54.390" end="01:54.700">ら</span><span begin="01:54.720" end="01:54.850">れ</span><span begin="01:54.890" end="01:55.100">な</span><span begin="01:55.100" end="01:55.220">い</span><span begin="01:55.560" end="01:56.200">空</span><span begin="01:56.240" end="01:56.950">白</span><span begin="01:56.980" end="01:57.130">の</span><span begin="01:57.170" end="01:57.640">中</span><span begin="01:57.670" end="01:58.200">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在什么也无法填满的空白之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在什麼也無法填滿的空白之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Inside a blank that nothing could ever fill</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">무엇으로도 메울 수 없는 공백 속에서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans ce blanc que rien ne peut combler</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En un vacío que nada puede llenar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In einer Leere die nichts ausfüllen kann</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Dentro de um vazio que nada pode preencher</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В пустоте которую ничем не заполнить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In un vuoto che nulla può colmare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nani mo umerarenai kuuhaku no naka de</span></p>
      <p begin="01:58.990" end="02:04.660" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:58.990" end="01:59.290">確</span><span begin="01:59.360" end="01:59.740">か</span><span begin="01:59.890" end="02:00.280">な</span><span begin="02:00.550" end="02:01.010">温</span><span begin="02:01.050" end="02:01.190">度</span><span begin="02:01.230" end="02:01.650">を</span><span begin="02:01.900" end="02:02.070">つ</span><span begin="02:02.070" end="02:02.280">よ</span><span begin="02:02.340" end="02:02.530">く</span><span begin="02:02.560" end="02:02.990">求</span><span begin="02:03.030" end="02:03.200">め</span><span begin="02:03.260" end="02:03.400">て</span><span begin="02:03.480" end="02:04.660">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我曾强烈追寻真实的温度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我曾強烈追尋真實的溫度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I was longing so fiercely for a certain warmth</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">분명한 온기를 간절히 바랐어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je cherchais ardemment une chaleur certaine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Buscaba con fuerza una temperatura cierta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Suchte ich verzweifelt nach einer wahrhaftigen Wärme</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu buscava intensamente uma temperatura real</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я отчаянно искала подлинное тепло</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Cercavo con forza un calore certo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tashika na ondo o tsuyoku motometeta</span></p>
      <p begin="02:05.860" end="02:11.100" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="02:05.860" end="02:06.090">ど</span><span begin="02:06.180" end="02:07.260">こ</span><span begin="02:07.260" end="02:07.420">ま</span><span begin="02:07.420" end="02:08.490">で</span><span begin="02:08.590" end="02:09.670">風</span><span begin="02:09.960" end="02:10.280">を</span><span begin="02:10.340" end="02:10.680">追</span><span begin="02:10.680" end="02:10.840">っ</span><span begin="02:10.840" end="02:11.100">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论要追逐风到何方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論要追逐風到何方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">No matter how far I chase the wind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어디까지 바람을 따라가도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Jusqu'où puis je poursuivre le vent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por más lejos que persiga el viento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie weit ich auch dem Wind nachjage</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Até onde perseguirei o vento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Как далеко я буду гнаться за ветром</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Fin dove inseguirò il vento</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Doko made kaze o otte</span></p>
      <p begin="02:11.330" end="02:16.550" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="02:11.330" end="02:12.660">傷</span><span begin="02:12.720" end="02:12.910">つ</span><span begin="02:12.910" end="02:14.030">い</span><span begin="02:14.090" end="02:14.200">て</span><span begin="02:14.280" end="02:15.500">も</span><span begin="02:15.640" end="02:15.750">止</span><span begin="02:15.800" end="02:15.990">ま</span><span begin="02:15.990" end="02:16.130">れ</span><span begin="02:16.160" end="02:16.320">な</span><span begin="02:16.320" end="02:16.550">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">即使遍体鳞伤也无法停下</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">即使遍體鱗傷也無法停下</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if I am wounded I cannot stop</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">상처 입어도 멈출 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même blessée je ne peux m'arrêter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque me hiera no puedo detenerme</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Selbst verletzt kann ich nicht stehen bleiben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo ferida não consigo parar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже ранясь не смогу остановиться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Per quanto ferita non posso fermarmi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kizutsuite mo tomarenai</span></p>
      <p begin="02:16.820" end="02:22.320" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="02:16.820" end="02:18.200">僕</span><span begin="02:18.230" end="02:18.340">の</span><span begin="02:18.400" end="02:19.550">ま</span><span begin="02:19.600" end="02:19.730">ま</span><span begin="02:19.760" end="02:20.560">で</span><span begin="02:20.940" end="02:21.120">い</span><span begin="02:21.240" end="02:21.640">つ</span><span begin="02:21.780" end="02:22.320">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">总有一天我想以真实的自己</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">總有一天我想以真實的自己</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Someday as myself</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나 그대로 언젠가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En restant moi même un jour</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Siendo yo misma algún día</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eines Tages will ich so wie ich bin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sendo eu mesma um dia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Однажды оставаясь собой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Restando me stessa un giorno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku no mama de itsuka</span></p>
      <p begin="02:22.660" end="02:30.850" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="02:22.660" end="02:23.010">た</span><span begin="02:23.010" end="02:23.140">だ</span><span begin="02:23.180" end="02:23.440">ひ</span><span begin="02:23.560" end="02:23.770">と</span><span begin="02:23.850" end="02:23.970">つ</span><span begin="02:24.040" end="02:24.500">と</span><span begin="02:24.730" end="02:25.010">出</span><span begin="02:25.010" end="02:25.230">会</span><span begin="02:25.230" end="02:25.340">い</span><span begin="02:25.430" end="02:26.970">た</span><span begin="02:26.970" end="02:27.050">い</span><span begin="02:27.490" end="02:27.730">こ</span><span begin="02:27.830" end="02:28.380">こ</span><span begin="02:28.500" end="02:30.850">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在这里遇见那唯一之物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在這裡遇見那唯一之物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to meet the one and only thing here</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이곳에서 단 하나와 만나고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux rencontrer l'unique chose ici</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero encontrar aquí lo único verdadero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hier der Einzigen begegnen die alles bedeutet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero encontrar aqui algo único</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я хочу встретить здесь единственное</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio incontrare quell unica cosa qui</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tada hitotsu to deaitai koko ni</span></p>
      <p begin="02:39.130" end="02:44.230" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="02:39.130" end="02:40.480">誰</span><span begin="02:40.530" end="02:40.970">に</span><span begin="02:41.190" end="02:41.570">知</span><span begin="02:41.570" end="02:41.880">ら</span><span begin="02:41.880" end="02:42.490">れ</span><span begin="02:42.550" end="02:43.230">ず</span><span begin="02:43.290" end="02:43.910">と</span><span begin="02:43.960" end="02:44.230">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">即使不为任何人所知</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">即使不為任何人所知</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if no one ever knows</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">누구에게도 알려지지 않아도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si personne ne le sait</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque nadie llegue a saberlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch wenn niemand davon erfährt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo sem que ninguém saiba</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пусть никто об этом не узнает</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se nessuno lo saprà</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dare ni shirarezu tomo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:44.620" end="02:51.570" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="02:44.620" end="02:45.360">消</span><span begin="02:45.360" end="02:45.970">え</span><span begin="02:46.010" end="02:46.690">な</span><span begin="02:46.690" end="02:46.950">い</span><span begin="02:47.220" end="02:48.090">詩</span><span begin="02:48.090" end="02:48.370">を</span><span begin="02:48.590" end="02:49.340">記</span><span begin="02:49.410" end="02:51.570">す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">也要写下不会消失的诗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">也要寫下不會消失的詩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I will write a poem that will not disappear</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사라지지 않을 시를 새겨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'inscris un poème qui ne disparaîtra pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Escribo un poema que no se borrará</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schreibe ich ein Gedicht das nie vergeht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Registro um poema que não desaparecerá</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я запишу песнь что не исчезнет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Scriverò una poesia che non svanirà</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kienai uta o shirusu</span></p>
      <p begin="02:52.480" end="02:57.730" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="02:52.480" end="02:52.850">終</span><span begin="02:52.850" end="02:53.880">わ</span><span begin="02:53.880" end="02:53.980">り</span><span begin="02:54.080" end="02:55.030">の</span><span begin="02:55.240" end="02:55.390">な</span><span begin="02:55.390" end="02:56.210">い</span><span begin="02:56.590" end="02:57.400">創</span><span begin="02:57.470" end="02:57.730">造</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无尽的创造</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無盡的創造</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">An endless creation</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">끝없는 창조</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Une création sans fin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Una creación sin final</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eine Schöpfung ohne Ende</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Uma criação sem fim</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Бесконечное творение</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Una creazione senza fine</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Owari no nai souzou</span></p>
      <p begin="02:58.010" end="03:03.210" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="02:58.010" end="02:59.570">心</span><span begin="02:59.570" end="03:00.610">は</span><span begin="03:00.740" end="03:01.980">もう</span><span begin="03:02.250" end="03:02.470">知</span><span begin="03:02.470" end="03:02.620">っ</span><span begin="03:02.620" end="03:02.780">て</span><span begin="03:02.780" end="03:02.890">い</span><span begin="03:02.950" end="03:03.210">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">心早已知晓</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">心早已知曉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">My heart already knew</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">마음은 이미 알고 있었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mon cœur le savait déjà</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mi corazón ya lo sabía</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mein Herz hatte es längst gewusst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Meu coração já sabia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сердце уже знало</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il cuore ormai lo sapeva</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kokoro wa mou shitte ita</span></p>
      <p begin="03:03.490" end="03:10.400" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="03:03.490" end="03:03.720">こ</span><span begin="03:03.790" end="03:04.830">こ</span><span begin="03:04.860" end="03:05.010">に</span><span begin="03:05.010" end="03:06.200">い</span><span begin="03:06.200" end="03:06.290">る</span><span begin="03:06.350" end="03:07.280">と</span><span begin="03:07.560" end="03:08.390">叫</span><span begin="03:08.480" end="03:08.930">び</span><span begin="03:09.280" end="03:09.760">続</span><span begin="03:09.830" end="03:10.070">け</span><span begin="03:10.170" end="03:10.400">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不断呐喊着我就在这里</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不斷吶喊著我就在這裡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It keeps crying out that I am here</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">여기에 있다고 계속 외치며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je continue de crier que je suis ici</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sigo gritando que estoy aquí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es schreit weiter dass ich hier bin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Continuo gritando que estou aqui</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я продолжаю кричать что я здесь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Continuando a gridare che sono qui</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koko ni iru to sakebitsuzukete</span></p>
      <p begin="03:10.480" end="03:14.640" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="03:10.480" end="03:11.030">青</span><span begin="03:11.080" end="03:11.150">く</span><span begin="03:11.390" end="03:11.610">燃</span><span begin="03:11.610" end="03:11.860">え</span><span begin="03:11.860" end="03:11.960">る</span><span begin="03:12.030" end="03:13.470">火</span><span begin="03:13.780" end="03:14.000">の</span><span begin="03:14.100" end="03:14.480">よう</span><span begin="03:14.480" end="03:14.640">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">如同青蓝燃烧的火焰</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">如同青藍燃燒的火焰</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Like a flame burning blue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">푸르게 타오르는 불꽃처럼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme une flamme bleue qui brûle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como una llama que arde azul</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie eine Flamme die blau brennt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como uma chama que arde em azul</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно пламя горящее синим</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come un fuoco che arde azzurro</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aoku moeru hi no you ni</span></p>
      <p begin="03:14.780" end="03:18.890" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="03:14.780" end="03:15.320">誰</span><span begin="03:15.320" end="03:15.560">も</span><span begin="03:15.630" end="03:15.930">い</span><span begin="03:15.980" end="03:16.200">な</span><span begin="03:16.200" end="03:16.580">い</span><span begin="03:16.830" end="03:17.050">絵</span><span begin="03:17.100" end="03:17.300">の</span><span begin="03:17.330" end="03:18.890">中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在无人之画中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在無人之畫中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Inside a picture without anyone</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아무도 없는 그림 속에서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans une image sans personne</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dentro de una pintura sin nadie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In einem Bild ohne irgendwen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Dentro de uma pintura sem ninguém</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В картине где никого нет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dentro un quadro senza nessuno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dare mo inai e no naka</span></p>
      <p begin="03:19.530" end="03:23.330" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="03:19.530" end="03:19.900">夜</span><span begin="03:19.940" end="03:20.070">が</span><span begin="03:20.070" end="03:20.490">明</span><span begin="03:20.560" end="03:20.750">け</span><span begin="03:20.770" end="03:23.330">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">夜色迎来黎明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">夜色迎來黎明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The night breaks into dawn</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">밤이 밝아 와</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La nuit se lève</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Amanece la noche</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bricht die Nacht zum Morgen auf</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A noite amanhece</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Наступает рассвет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Si fa giorno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yo ga akeru</span></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</tt>
